snippet.title: QubiQuest: Castle Craft - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Watch the announcement trailer for QubiQuest: Castle Craft, an upcoming game featuring a blend of voxel sandbox, action, and horde defense. In QubiQuest: Castle Craft, players build huge castles in an ancient war-torn world and defend them against hordes of enemies in chaotic siege battles of epic proportions. QubiQuest: Castle Craft is coming to PC in 2023.
